{"tid":1745751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請和理非做文宣幫前線增加支持度","createTime":"2019-11-22T11:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:20:45.000Z","uid":61886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c1cd9ae8b20c7779b23c019f13f28e9b2d03e0f9","tid":1745751,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:18:43.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得<br />\n做文宣就係為咗跳出同溫層<br />\n去爭取更加多支持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2yomas0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2yomas0.png&h=ecbaa1d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最近我哋文宣明顯少咗好多<br />\n支持度亦有所減少<br />\n好多連儂牆俾人徹底清走<br />\n<br />\n如果我哋繼續大安旨意 等前線幫我地擋子彈<br />\n我哋嘅支持度只會越來越少<br />\n最終步向失敗<br />\n<br />\n和理非們請出一分力<br />\n我哋連儂牆講明 撕一貼百<br />\n今晚每人帶幾張文宣<br />\n去重建連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n希望聽朝起身見到連儂牆<br />\n係比之前更壯觀 <br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"d7919b0c73d2c7abe87ef641ec0e66dd8a4bb96f","tid":1745751,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:19:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd1c6875d1bdcb12c4acefdd5e7128e9733d7a45","tid":1745751,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"push"}]}